entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: The Selonians are faced with a well organized group of smugglers. You don't know how they coerced the Selonians into working for them, but you can find out more by following the Selonian's requests.
entries.journal_entry_description: The CorSec agent cannot officially intervene in the affairs of the Selonian den. You have been asked to see what an independent agent could do for them.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find Kiki the Selonian and see how you can help her against the smugglers.
